This paper deals with coding theory, which is a subfield of information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the weight distribution of cyclic codes, which is a topic in algebraic coding theory (cs.GT). Additionally, the paper mentions applications in consumer electronics, data storage systems, and communication systems, which are areas of interest in distributed systems (cs.DS), cryptography (cs.CR), and signal processing (cs.SI).
